⊢ source
  yield text

  ⊢= text ← "Cell is a self-bootstrapping metacircular language for LLMs. Programs are documents. Execution fills in values. The document IS the program IS the state. Cells start as natural language (soft) and progressively crystallize into deterministic code (hard) under oracle pressure. Cell is the Scheme of LLMs."

  yield text ≡ "Cell is a self-bootstrapping metacircular language for LLMs. Programs are documents. Execution fills in values. The document IS the program IS the state. Cells start as natural language (soft) and progressively crystallize into deterministic code (hard) under oracle pressure. Cell is the Scheme of LLMs."

